The paper discusses the security and privacy concerns related to biometric authentication, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for biometric authentication, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the challenges of biometric authentication, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
